data.description: Embrace the harmonious blend of nature and comfort in this idyllic countryside cottage nestled on over 1 acre of land, ideal for animals, gardens, and all of your toys. Conveniently situated mere minutes from Highway 50, yet cocooned in the tranquility of the woods, it offers a perfect blend of accessibility and seclusion. This 2-bedroom, 1-bath home boasts a sprawling deck that overlooks a fenced backyard, complemented by a flourishing apple tree. Step inside to discover the warmth of engineered hickory hardwood floors, maple cabinets, and a fireplace to keep you warm and cozy. Additionally, the expansive storage space beneath the house adds practicality to this charming home.
